title: IAA Tonight | Niners Preview & Thibodeaux's Knee Injury
description: We continue our Countdown to Kickoff with a stop in San Francisco to preview the 49ers. Can Trey Lance take the Niners to the next level? Also, the crew discusses NY Giants rookie Kayvon Thibodeaux's knee injury due to a cut block by the Bengals' Thaddeus Moss.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Adam 'Pac Man' Jones, Brandon Flowers)
